https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g9WtA-XUeGs&t=18s -- Dynamo DB


Scale seamlessly - Lambda scales up and down automatically to handle your workloads, and you don't pay anything when your code isn't running.

Lambda is a Serverless Architecture.  Code run without provisioning and manage Server

Features
1. Serverless - You no need to manage any server
2. Event Driven - Function trigger various aws services like S3, dynamodb, kinesis, SNS, API, gateway
3. Auto scaling - Lambda automatic scaling
4. pay-as-go service - pay for the code run
5. Support multiple language - Java, Python, nodejs, RUBY, GO

How it works
------------
upload a code 
set up Trigger / Destination
Execution
